text SilphCo_7F_Text_HaveMonForSavingUs {
	"Oh! Hi! You're not a ROCKET!
	You came to save us?
	Why, thank you!

	I want you to have this POKéMON
	for saving us."
}

text SilphCo_7F_Text_ObtainedLaprasFromEmployee {
	"{PLAYER} obtained a LAPRAS from
	the SILPH employee!"
}

text SilphCo_7F_Text_ExplainLapras {
	"It's a LAPRAS.
	It's a very intelligent POKéMON.

	We kept it in our lab, but it will
	be much better off with you.

	I think you will be a good TRAINER
	for LAPRAS!

	It's a good swimmer.
	It'll give you a lift across water!"
}

text SilphCo_7F_Text_RocketBossWentToBoardroom {
	"TEAM ROCKET's BOSS went to the
	boardroom!

	Is our PRESIDENT okay?
	I'm worried."
}

text SilphCo_7F_Text_RocketsAfterMasterBall {
	"TEAM ROCKET was after the MASTER
	BALL, which catches any POKéMON."
}

text SilphCo_7F_Text_CanceledMasterBallProject {
	"We canceled the MASTER BALL
	project because of TEAM ROCKET."
}

text SilphCo_7F_Text_BadIfTeamRocketTookOver {
	"It would be bad if TEAM ROCKET
	took over SILPH or our POKéMON."
}

text SilphCo_7F_Text_WowYouChasedOffTeamRocket {
	"Wow!

	You chased off TEAM ROCKET all by
	yourself?"
}

text SilphCo_7F_Text_ReallyDangerousHere {
	"You!
	It's really dangerous here!

	You came to save me?
	You can't!"
}

text SilphCo_7F_Text_ThankYouSoMuch {
	"Thank you so much!"
}

text SilphCo_7F_Text_Grunt3Intro {
	"Uh-oh!
	I smell a little mouse!"
}

text SilphCo_7F_Text_Grunt3Defeat {
	"Lights out!"
}

text SilphCo_7F_Text_Grunt3PostBattle {
	"You won't find my BOSS by just
	scurrying around!"
}

text SilphCo_7F_Text_JoshuaIntro {
	"Heheh!

	You mistook me for a SILPH worker?"
}

text SilphCo_7F_Text_JoshuaDefeat {
	"I'm done!"
}

text SilphCo_7F_Text_JoshuaPostBattle {
	"Despite your age, you are a
	skilled TRAINER!"
}

text SilphCo_7F_Text_Grunt1Intro {
	"I am one of the four ROCKET
	BROTHERS!"
}

text SilphCo_7F_Text_Grunt1Defeat {
	"Aack!
	Brothers, I lost!"
}

text SilphCo_7F_Text_Grunt1PostBattle {
	"Doesn't matter.
	My brothers will repay the favor!"
}

text SilphCo_7F_Text_Grunt2Intro {
	"A child intruder?
	That must be you!"
}

text SilphCo_7F_Text_Grunt2Defeat {
	"Fine!
	I lost!"
}

text SilphCo_7F_Text_Grunt2PostBattle {
	"Go on home before my BOSS gets
	ticked off!"
}

text SilphCo_7F_Text_RivalWhatKeptYou {
	"{RIVAL}: What kept you, {PLAYER}?"
}

text SilphCo_7F_Text_RivalIntro {
	"{RIVAL}: Hahaha! I thought you'd
	turn up if I waited here!

	I guess TEAM ROCKET slowed you
	down! Not that I care!

	I saw you in SAFFRON, so I decided
	to see if you got better!"
}

text SilphCo_7F_Text_RivalDefeat {
	"Oh, man!
	So, you are ready for BOSS
	ROCKET!"
}

text SilphCo_7F_Text_RivalPostBattle {
	"Well, {PLAYER}!
	I'm moving on up and ahead!

	By checking my POKéDEX, I'm
	starting to see what's strong and
	how they evolve!

	Am I a genius or what?

	I'm going to the POKéMON LEAGUE to
	boot out the ELITE FOUR.

	I'll become the world's most
	powerful TRAINER!

	{PLAYER}, well, good luck to you!
	Don't sweat it!
	Smell ya!"
}

text SilphCo_7F_Text_FloorSign {
	"SILPH CO. HEAD OFFICE
	7F"
}
